305
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:57,710
Cleaning.

306
00:16:57,710 --> 00:16:59,120
It's kinda fun.

307
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,390
Wanna try it out, Nami?

308
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:02,730
What's all the noise?

309
00:17:03,810 --> 00:17:06,710
What? The Silky Smooth Skin Soap?

310
00:17:06,710 --> 00:17:08,590
Hey, that's dangerous!

311
00:17:08,590 --> 00:17:10,640
Don't worry! We're fine!

312
00:17:14,320 --> 00:17:15,080
Luffy!

313
00:17:17,120 --> 00:17:18,200
