322
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:48,390
So that's what you were up to?

323
00:17:48,390 --> 00:17:49,700
That's right.

324
00:17:49,700 --> 00:17:55,820
It is a one of a kind map recording our travels on the Grand Line.

325
00:17:55,820 --> 00:17:57,110
That's all I wanted!

326
00:17:58,970 --> 00:18:03,280
My dream is to complete my own map of the world.

327
00:18:06,140 --> 00:18:07,600
Get out!

328
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:08,760
But...

329
00:18:08,760 --> 00:18:09,670
Just...

330
00:18:09,670 --> 00:18:10,280
Nami!

331
00:18:10,890 --> 00:18:11,740
What?

332
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:12,510
Sorry.

333
00:18:12,510 --> 00:18:14,950
If sorry was all it took, the Marines wouldn't be after us!

334
00:18:14,950 --> 00:18:16,140
Just get out!

335
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:20,340
If you don't leave, I'll fine you 100,000 beri!

336
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:24,550
It's your fault.

337
00:18:24,550 --> 00:18:25,870
Why me?

338
00:18:25,870 --> 00:18:28,700
Geez, they'll just be in my way if they stay in here.

339
00:18:28,700 --> 00:18:30,590
Luffy, cheer up!

340
