360
00:19:49,780 --> 00:19:51,470
Am I a genius or what?

361
00:19:52,190 --> 00:19:52,980
What was that?

362
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:55,960
Hey, what's going on!?

363
00:19:57,110 --> 00:19:58,040
Nami!

364
00:19:58,040 --> 00:20:00,480
Hey, what are you doing?

365
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:03,670
