366
00:20:06,100 --> 00:20:09,400
But, the 100,000 beri fine...

367
00:20:11,010 --> 00:20:12,380
Don't be stupid.

368
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:14,720
Hey, you guys!

369
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,370
