375
00:20:22,420 --> 00:20:24,590
Luffy, Zoro! Hoist the sails!

376
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:25,610
Aye!

377
00:20:25,610 --> 00:20:28,890
Usopp, Chopper! Tie down everything on deck with the ropes!

378
00:20:28,890 --> 00:20:29,950
Got it!

379
00:20:29,950 --> 00:20:31,610
Sanji-kun, hard to starboard!

380
