388
00:21:12,900 --> 00:21:14,220
Nice work!

389
00:21:14,220 --> 00:21:15,730
You can all take a rest now!

390
00:21:15,730 --> 00:21:17,080
Oh.

391
00:21:17,080 --> 00:21:20,830
I'm going to continue with my maps, so keep watching the clouds, okay?

392
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:22,540
